-- Germany’s Ex-Soccer Captain Ballack Retires Aged 36, FAZ Reports
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-10-02T15:01:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-02/germany-s-ex-soccer-captain-ballack-retires-aged-36-faz-reports.html
Germany’s former national soccer team
captain  Michael Ballack  has retired with immediate effect at age
36, Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung reported, citing the player’s
lawyer.  Ballack, who had been linked with a club in Australia,
played his last professional game for German league team Bayer
Leverkusen on May 5, FAZ said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Webb in Frankfurt at 
